Bee Love is the Davis Bee Charmer and founder of the Davis Bee Sanctuary and Bee Love School of Permaculture.  He is an active resident of Village Homes and advocate for pollinators, community building, gardens, and abundant living. He is passionate about establishing the new paradigm of peace on earth and does through rebuilding our relationship with bees and other pollinators and using permaculture design to holistically design a resilient abundant ecosystem that provides for everyones needs while caring for the earth, the people, and sharing surplus.

